  (text "CARRIER POWER NOTES:\\nTPS54331DR: VIN 7-24V → +5V/3A, 570kHz\\n  R_P2=100kΩ → 570kHz. R_P3=1.0MΩ R_P4=196kΩ → Vout=4.98V\\n  L_P1 SRR1260A-100M 10µH/3A. D_P1 SS34 catch diode.\\n  PH node: minimize copper area to reduce EMI\\nAMS1117-3.3: +5V→+3V3, 800mA rated, ~570mA load with 2x margin\\nDual VIN: J_VIN_JACK (barrel primary) + J_VIN_TERM (screw alt)\\nHUB75 panel power: isolated from carrier VIN path\\n  C_P11 1000µF handles LED switching inrush on large panels\\nFB1 BLM15AX601SN1D: +3V3→AVDD for ES8388 analog supply"
    (at 20 130 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "8313ae29-f152-4964-849e-1b7ac5dacca2")
